<!DOCTYPE>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>DevBoard</title>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.2.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascript/home.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascript/script.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/catalog.css">
  </head>
  <body onload="getBoardListHome(), getPopulairThreads(), getStats()">

    <div id="header">
      <div id="title">
        <img src="/images/logo.png">
        <h1>DevBoard</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="content">
      <div id="info">
        <div class="box">
          <div class="bar">
            <h3>What is DevBoard?</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="boxcontent">
            DevBoard is a simple image-based bulletin board where anyone can post
            comments and share images. There are boards dedicated to a variety
            of topics. Users do not need to register an account before
            participating in the community. Feel free to click on a board below
            that interests you and jump right in!
            <br/>
            DevBoard differentiates itself from other imageboards by using only
            homebrew opensource software, for wich you can find the source at the
            bottom of the page.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="board" class="box">
        <div class="bar">
          <h3>Boards</h3>
        </div>
        <div id="boardlist" class="boxcontent">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="thread" class="box">
        <div class="bar">
          <h3>Populair Threads</h3>
        </div>
        <ul id="threads">
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div id="stat" class="box">
        <div class="bar">
          <h3>Stats</h3>
        </div>
        <div id="statcontent" class="boxcontent">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr>
    <div id="footer">
      <div id="credits">
        Imageboard based on <a href="https://github.com/MeesCode/DevBoard">DevBoard</a> by Mees Brinkhuis.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
